data.text:
I love laughing at my own jokes: Zervaan Bunshah

TNN / Jun 30, 2024, 16:43 (IST)

We're diving into the comedic mind of someone who's been making waves with their rapid-fire humour and unique style. Zervaan Bunshah, known for his sharp wit and quick delivery, has been delighting audiences with his daily uploads and infectious energy. Moreover, he is also known for Aarya (2020), Summer Afternoon (2022) and FilterCopy Talkies (2018). Read on for his fun interview.

Wayne Brady identifies as pansexual, says, "Right now, this is the proper place for me"

etimes.in / Aug 08, 2023, 12:47 (IST)

The popular actor, comedian, singer, and host of improv comedy programmes including Whose Line is it Anyway and Let's Make a Deal has now openly admitted to being pansexual. The 51-year-old actor was previously wed to Diana Lasso and Mandie Taketa. His marriages to Diana and Mandie both ended in divorce in 1995 and 2007, respectively.

Kevin Conroy, voice of Batman passes away at 66; Mark Hamill says 'He will always be my Batman'

AP / Nov 12, 2022, 02:24 (IST)

Kevin Conroy, the prolific voice actor whose gravely delivery on "Batman: The Animated Series" was for many Batman fans the definitive sound of the Caped Crusader, has died at 66.

Whoopi Goldberg had elevator 'fart war' with Robin Williams, Billy Crystal

IANS / Aug 09, 2022, 16:05 (IST)

Hollywood actress Whoopi Goldberg was once involved in an elevator "fart war" with late star Robin Williams and actor Billy Crystal, according to her granddaughter.

Jumanji-themed amusement park in works

ANI / Mar 18, 2022, 18:17 (IST)

If you are a 'Jumanji' lover, then ready to experience the magic of the popular movie franchise via an amusement park.

Robert Downey Jr. channels Tony Stark as he honours Scarlett Johansson in a witty message

PTI / Nov 23, 2021, 17:58 (IST)

Robert Downey Jr was at his wittiest and funniest best as he praised his good friend and Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU) co-star Scarlett Johansson during the annual American Cinematheque Award ceremony.

Matt Damon reveals he has a private Instagram account

ANI / Sep 11, 2021, 17:34 (IST)

Hollywood actor Matt Damon recently revealed that he does have "a very private Instagram account" he mainly uses to keep up with close friends.

Things to keep in mind while bringing up a teenage boy!

TNN / Sep 01, 2021, 16:26 (IST)

Dealing with teenage boys can be difficult, but you also need to understand that they are going through a phase where they want to be heard and understood

Prolific actor and director Norman Lloyd dies at age 106

Reuters / May 12, 2021, 09:53 (IST)

American actor, producer and director Norman Lloyd, whose career of more than 80 years included collaborations with legends such as Charlie Chaplin and Orson Welles, has died at the age of 106, Variety and Deadline Hollywood reported on Tuesday.

Zelda Williams celebrates father Robin Williams' 69th birthday by helping homeless shelters

TIMESOFINDIA.COM / Jul 22, 2020, 12:59 (IST)

One of Hollywood's most popular actors, Robin Williams, who committed suicide in 2014 was reported to be suffering from dementia, would have turned 69 today.
